Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:44.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:44.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:58.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:58.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:37.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:37.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years have passed since the \NWar of the Best in Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew each \Ncompleted individual training
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and boarded the newly coated Sunny \Nsetting sail for the Fish-Man Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...located 10,000 meters below the sea level...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to go on to the \Nnext stage - the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the extra-vehicular Flutter Kick Coating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra-vehicular diving suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You have to attach the safety rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:44.55,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Lost in the Deep Sea! \NThe Straw Hats Get Separated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament; Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel weak because of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that octopus! Is it trying to stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, Sanji-san got out of the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really fast! \NHe's like a Fish-Man! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been running and running
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to get away from those hideous people for 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the monster is nothing.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually looks rather cute to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bien Cuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Grill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style technique;\N Crossing the Six Paths!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon that rules the\N realm of water... So weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel grateful when I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to fight every single day for the past 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To top him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still gonna get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I couldn't see his movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something, No. 7?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll kill you!\N--Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, Zoro! Sanji! You can't cut his arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blew it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten so much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while he's in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Something is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A shark?\N--Isn't that shark wearing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fairly big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanking us for helping him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a polite shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being drawn into the sea current!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, let's go back to Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been swept away \Nby the downward current!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Follow them! We have to stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't wanna die here!\N--You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're still here?\N--You're too calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are spinning! But I don't have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the yard level! Hard to Port! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash into the continental shelf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose your concentration,\N or the ship will wreck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get thrown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in the center of the current!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you all so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I know! You guys can't \Ndo anything without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find Luffy and the \Nother two. We got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they haven't been \Nshredded to pieces by the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your imagination is terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark - I wanna look for \Nthem but I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with darkness.\N I feel something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably submerged around 7,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Shark Submerge can't\N take the pressure this deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we near the Fish-Man Island?\N Maybe they got there already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie-chan said it's located \Nat 10,000 meters below sea level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to submerge 3,000 meters more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All they have is a small bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're alive, \Nthere isn't enough air so it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told them to \Nattach the safety rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't accomplish anything\N standing around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for them. I now have a search light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nipple Lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be looking for us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Zoro-san! Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this vast, submerged expanse,\N the Sunny Eyes don't help that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness is stirring up our anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, we're not getting \Nanywhere. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop the ship so try\N not to overlook anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be some trace of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a jellyfish! There's a \Nmassive jellyfish above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's huge! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're twinkling! Like stars in the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a tentacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably venomous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jellyfish got eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we lost some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better than getting eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Burst is a weapon that\N shoots a fair amount of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since we're in the water, \Nwe only have a limited amount of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when we shoot the air \Nout, the bubble shrinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But it makes me nervous \Nto see the bubble shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fish that got bitten\N turned upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they contain a neurotoxin as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deep sea's scary! It's dark too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of fish with \Nwhite eyes... It's creepy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the deep sea is always dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthere are many creatures with rudimentary eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they can't see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools! See this? Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are some with developed eyes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? How can I see things without eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you people wanna know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is... Tum, tum, tum, tum, tum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I'm used to being lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop fooling around and look for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I get hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Sanji! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rope must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen that pirate guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, he's still here! \NI totally forgot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him since we got this deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he got thrown off \Nduring the downward pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hands and legs were tied up so \Nhe couldn't hold on to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he untied himself. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, he's somewhere\Non the ship? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to be hiding somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sneak into the girls' room--\N if that's what you want, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We have enough problems already
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut now we have to look out for him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! He's not that strong anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those formidable 3 who were fighting\N against the Kraken went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they could have \Nsurvived after getting lost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with just those bubbles to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that I couldn't kill Straw Hat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can prove that he's dead by killing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthese crewmembers and taking their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't rush, Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill them here, there's no one else to sail the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They navigate the ship pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you get to the Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you all will be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh no! Shoot! Dammit!\N--Now he can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he get in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't paying attention. If he \Nwasn't so stupid, we could be in danger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body wasn't taking form.\NIt has melted like mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Like mud?\N--Yeah, I'm sure it's a Devil Fruit power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've eaten a Logia-type fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was only pretending to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get me out of here, mister!\N Mister in swimshorts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become your servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I feel hot all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this? Smoke? \NIt's blocking our view forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke from the sea floor? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hydrothermal deposits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A volcanic area in the sea!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you can see that there \Nwere volcanic eruptions here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from here! \NIf it erupts, we're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot... It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carnivorous Tubeworms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faceless Crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deep sea's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others can't survive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get sad. \NI finally got to see him after 2 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! They're not gonna die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used Coup de Burst little by \Nlittle but we lost so much air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! It's so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Fish-Man Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Luffy and the others are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't submerged \Nanother 3,000 meters yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"WHO-ARE-YOU?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you sending \Nthe flashing signals with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you see anything?\N--No, it's still too bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an angler! He tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fooled by the deep-sea hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally trapped! Can we get away...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster in the sea that looks like a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Sea Bonze!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna capsize the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ankoro! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat ships! How many \Ntimes do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vander Decken-sama won't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did he help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We have to get away \Nanyway! He is a monster too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The infamous ghost ship, the Flying Dutchman,\N emerges from the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But suddenly, a submarine volcano erupts,\N creating yet more danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evading falling rocks, \Nthey make it to the ocean floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where a scenery not expected \Nin the Deep Sea awaits them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undersea Volcanic Eruption!\N Drifting to the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
